{
  "stem": "20142.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But since he refused to give me any help except providing some clothing and-- and some help of contacting people to get me through the sewer lines, that's all what he could do.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he told me what he going to do and how that's-- how would it be done.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sosnowski.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-O-S-N-O-W-S-K-I.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were trying to get anybody who was capable of getting out-- out of the camps to give them another chance in life, I guess.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or maybe what the work that I'd done before for them for distributing the leaflets and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To the contrary, they told me that you have to realize that we only can get you out on this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then you will be on-- all on your own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I accepted-- I thought perhaps if I wouldn't have been shot, I probably would have gone into the woods and joined the partisans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But due to the fact that I was shot, I just lost consciousness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Coincidental fact that I did survive escaping from Majdanek gave me enough courage to continue going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The farmer asked me if there is any place in Warsaw that he want to deliver-- to bring me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I mentioned this place of-- and father's name-- father's friend's name Sosnowski.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this Sosnowski, he evidently was connected with some people who had underground activities or-- or knowledge, because two days later, after sleeping for two solid days, and just having minimum food to share with and a warm bowl of good soup that I will never forget in my life, two men came.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sosnowski came to me and said, tomorrow morning at 5 o'clock I will wake you up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Be prepared to leave immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, where am I going?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
